        {
            "title": "歐洲最大種子輪！前DeepMind核心研究員新創 完成11億美元融資 估值飆破50億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EjcvACXAO5IhH4FQrjBWuw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/cnyes_hk_559/cc33c9b7428ecdd674602e1a3dea1225\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
